ing: 1 (5.1 ounce) package instant vanilla pudding mix
des: "I whipped this up when I did not want to serve just plain old vanilla pudding. It was a smash!! I just smiled when the raves poured in, because prep took no time at all."
ins:
Mix dry pudding mix in a bowl with cinnamon, nutmeg, cloves, and ginger until well blended. Whisk in milk, stirring 2 minutes, or until no lumps remain.
Pour pudding into serving dishes and refrigerate 2 hours, or until set.
